<br>
I use Cleave because I have 52 modified parry: 17+17 parry, Moparry 3 and capped Dex. And I land Cleave almost as much as plague, which is one of the most damaging Axe styles there is.<br>
<br>
And for you skalds that are under the assumption parry is useless (/boggle) I would use Havoc/Plague as a backup and Evernight/Arctic rift on runners.<br>
 <br>
