<br>
Because Glacial hits harder than evernight, and 9 times out of 10 you're not landing arctic rift on anyone with good defense. I learned this the hard way. <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :p --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/tongue.gif ALT=":p"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  <br>
<br>
&quot;Also how do you go about kiteing a Nightshade exactly?&quot;<br>
